
<p>From&nbsp;<a href="https://fortune.com/2025/07/16/delta-moves-toward-eliminating-set-prices-in-favor-of-ai-that-determines-how-much-you-personally-will-pay-for-a-ticket/?utm_source=substack&amp;utm_medium=email">Fortune Magazine</a>:</p>



<blockquote class="wp-block-quote is-layout-flow wp-block-quote-is-layout-flow">
<p class="has-text-align-left">Delta has a long-term strategy to boost its profitability by moving away from set fares and toward individualized pricing using AI.&nbsp;The pilot program, which uses AI for 3% of fares, has so far been “amazingly favorable,” the airline said. Privacy advocates fear this will lead to price-gouging, with one consumer advocate comparing the tactic to “hacking our brains.”</p>
</blockquote>



